{"type":null,"faqId":7780,"title":"Ascend D1省电小窍门？","answer":"<p>\n\t可以直接开起设置中省电模式来省电。或者根据自己的需要手动关闭如下开关。<br />\n1、不使用手机时，按电源键关闭屏幕。<br />\n2、缩短屏幕待机时间：进入主菜单<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>设置<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>显示<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>屏幕超时。<br />\n3、降低屏幕亮度：进入主菜单<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>设置<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>显示<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>亮度。<br />\n4、关闭蓝牙和WLAN：进入主菜单<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>设置<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>无线和网络，取消勾选WLAN/蓝牙。<br />\n5、关闭后台数据同步：进入主菜单<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>设置<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>帐户与同步，取消勾选背景数据/自动同步。<br />\n6、关闭数据业务：进入主菜单<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>设置<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>无线和网络<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>移动网络，取消勾选已启用数据。<br />\n7、或者在通知栏中关闭数据开关。<br />\n8、关闭GPS：进入主菜单<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>设置<span style=\"layout-grid-mode:both;font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;\" lang=\"EN-US\">à</span>位置和安全，取消勾选使用GPS 卫星。\n</p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7920","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1343383607000,"seriesProductName":"U9500","visitedTimes":1301,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":30,"times":8,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.8,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}